prompts.frontCover: A whimsical and humorous botanical illustration for a greeting card, flat 2D vector art style. The scene features two charming, slightly frazzled-looking cartoon garden gnomes attempting to untangle a ridiculously long and knotted string of birthday bunting from a large, leafy monstera plant. One gnome is perched precariously on a mushroom, pulling one end of the bunting, while the other is on the ground, comically wrapped up in the string and leaves. The bunting is colorful with festive patterns. The entire illustration is framed by lush, elegant botanical elements like ferns, trailing ivy, and delicate wildflowers, rendered in a detailed yet clean illustrative style with a soft, natural color palette. Centered in a clear space amongst the foliage, the text "another year, another glorious mess" is written in a beautiful, flowing, and easily readable handwritten cursive script. The background is a clean, solid off-white color, making the vibrant illustration pop.
